message: Former Trump campaign chairman and Tea Party advocate Timothy Nolan has pleaded guilty to human trafficking and other charges.

data.description: Former Trump campaign chairman and Tea Party advocate Timothy Nolan has pleaded guilty to human trafficking and other charges. Nolan, 71, served as a district judge 40 years ago.
